  "beats": [
    {
      "zh": "尘途多倦，世事多艰，",
      "scene": "S2-01",
      "en": "Dusty roads tire us; the world is seldom easy."
    },
    {
      "zh": "奔波朝夕，前路漫漫。",
      "scene": "S2-01",
      "en": "We rush from dawn to dusk, with a long road ahead."
    },
    {
      "zh": "人世几番辗转，早已尝过冷暖悲欢。",
      "scene": "S2-01",
      "en": "After many turns in life, we have tasted both cold and warmth."
    },
    {
      "zh": "上念亲恩常记，",
      "scene": "S2-02",
      "en": "Above us stays the grace of our parents."
    },
    {
      "zh": "下思稚子相牵。",
      "scene": "S2-02",
      "en": "Below us are the small hands that still hold us close."
    },
    {
      "zh": "所以朝来躬身奔走，夜伴清灯自安。",
      "scene": "S2-02",
      "en": "So by day we labor on, and by night we sit quietly by the lamp."
    },
    {
      "zh": "有些疲惫，不必说出口；",
      "scene": "S2-03",
      "en": "Some weariness needs no telling."
    },
    {
      "zh": "有些艰难，也不必逢人细谈。",
      "scene": "S2-03",
      "en": "Some hardship need not be explained to everyone."
    },
    {
      "zh": "只因初心未改。",
      "scene": "S2-03",
      "en": "Because the first intention has not changed."
    },
    {
      "zh": "心里仍有要去的远山，",
      "scene": "S2-04",
      "en": "There is still a distant ridge the heart must reach."
    },
    {
      "zh": "纵然步履匆匆，",
      "scene": "S2-04",
      "en": "Though the steps remain hurried,"
    },
    {
      "zh": "也该向着光亮，一程一程地赶。",
      "scene": "S2-04",
      "en": "we should still move toward the light, one stretch at a time."
    },
    {
      "zh": "幸有人间烟火为伴，",
      "scene": "S2-05",
      "en": "Thankfully, the warmth of ordinary life keeps us company."
    },
    {
      "zh": "柴米灯火，亦能宽慰风霜。",
      "scene": "S2-05",
      "en": "Daily meals and lamplight can soften the frost of life."
    },
    {
      "zh": "平凡日子，也自有向前的力量。",
      "scene": "S2-05",
      "en": "Even plain days carry their own power to keep going."
    },
    {
      "zh": "愿你不言放弃，也敢迎风而立；",
      "scene": "S2-06",
      "en": "May you not speak of giving up, and still dare to face the wind."
    },
    {
      "zh": "把万般辛苦，慢慢酿成心安。",
      "scene": "S2-06",
      "en": "May all hardship slowly ripen into peace within."
    },
    {
      "zh": "纵前路仍远，也当昂首扬帆，逐光而攀。<END>",
      "scene": "S2-06",
      "en": "Though the road is still long, lift your sail and climb toward the light."
    }
  ],
